    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> October 16, 2024</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use krtk.rs, we store only the following information in our database:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Original URL:</strong> The URL you submit for shortening</li>
        <li><strong>Short URL:</strong> The shortened URL we generate</li>
        <li><strong>Timestamp:</strong> When the short URL was created</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not collect or store IP addresses, browser information, usage patterns, or any other personal data.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>The stored information is used solely to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide the URL shortening and redirection service</li>
        <li>Maintain the mapping between short and original URLs</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your data indefinitely unless manually deleted by the service operator. This is a demonstration application with no automated data deletion policies.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your information with any third parties.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>While we implement reasonable security measures, this is a demonstration service provided "as is" with no security guarantees.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request information about data we have stored or request deletion by contacting us through the information below.</p>

    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <div class="contact">
        <h2>8. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related questions or requests:</p>
        <p><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/darko-mesaros">https://github.com/darko-mesaros</a></p>
    </div>
